      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRONELLY TIMMY (2) was fresh up last time at Healesville where he finished seventh (20.55) in a T3 RSTW. Form here is sound including two wins. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. MACK IN BOOTS (1) finds it hard to win. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (22.61) at Ballarat. Has a good record at this journey. Must be included in calculations. KUEBIKO (3) took the sit on the lead from a low draw but levelled up and led around the bend to score (17.86) at Mt Gambier in a TG1-4W over 305m. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. BILLIES RAINBOW (6) has strong claims after a top-three finish at this track and distance last time out.",
